$$
\\begin{aligned}W &= m \\times g\\\\ m &= \\frac{W}{g}\\\\ m &= \\frac{980}{9.8} = 100\\ kg\\end{aligned}
$$
Thus, the mass of the object is $100\\ kg$.
`;
